<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1009835>
    dc:description "FIGURE 55. Shells of Metalycaeus species. A – C. Metalycaeus rathouisianus (Heude, 1882). A. syntype (SMF 39243) of M. rathouisianus. B. syntype (MCZ 167209) of Alycaeus dolomiticus Heude, 1890. C. MCZ 167222, labelled as Alycaeus neglectus Heude, 1886. D. Metalycaeus sinensis (Heude, 1882) (lectotype, MCZ 167216). E. Metalycaeus (?) ibex Páll- Gergely & Hunyadi n. sp., (holotype, MNHN IM- 2012 - 27042). Scale represents 5 mm. All photos: B. Páll-Gergely." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1009835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1009849>
    dc:description "FIGURE 63. Protoconchs of Metalycaeus species. A – B. Metalycaeus rathouisianus (Heude, 1882) (syntype of A. dolomiticus MCZ 167209). C – D. Metalycaeus oharai Páll-Gergely & Hunyadi n. sp. (holotype, HNHM 99712). All images: B. Páll- Gergely." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1009849/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1009853>
    dc:description "FIGURE 65. Opercula of Metalycaeus species. A – B. Metalycaeus rathouisianus (Heude, 1882) (MCZ 167209; syntype of Alycaeus dolomiticus). C – F. Metalycaeus (?) okuboi Páll-Gergely & Hunyadi, n. sp. (holotype, HNHM 99713). All images: B. Páll-Gergely." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1009853/files/figure.png" ;
